in der heym hob ikh geheysn Leyb Gilinski.

00:01:16.050 --> 00:01:18.200
ven hostu geborn?

00:01:18.944 --> 00:01:22.944
in s- zibetn monat

00:01:22.944 --> 00:01:26.610
eh eh fuftsn teg in zibetn monat.

00:01:26.624 --> 00:01:28.531
nayntsn fuftsn.

00:01:28.550 --> 00:01:30.150
AND vu?

00:01:30.000 --> 00:01:31.350
in Vilne.

00:01:31.250 --> 00:01:32.400
Vilne?

00:01:32.205 --> 00:01:34.100
Vilne, yo.

00:01:32.400 --> 00:01:34.450
Vilne hot geven...

00:01:34.350 --> 00:01:35.571
Rusland damolst.

00:01:35.050 --> 00:01:36.164
dem tsayt...

00:01:36.177 --> 00:01:38.446
in der tsayt, in nayntsn fuftsn, iz geven Rusland.

00:01:38.604 --> 00:01:44.800
du uh kenst mir d- zogn uh dayn uhm tates nomen ersht?

00:01:44.750 --> 00:01:46.150
ye, DAVID.

00:01:46.750 --> 00:01:47.940
DAVID?

00:01:47.950 --> 00:01:48.910
Gilinski

00:01:48.668 --> 00:01:49.455
Gilinski?

00:01:49.266 --> 00:01:49.926
YES.

00:01:49.941 --> 00:01:52.100
AND dayn muter?

00:01:51.844 --> 00:01:53.200
Leye.

00:01:53.450 --> 00:01:57.750
Gilinski, ven zi hot geheyrat. far dem hot zi geheysn Leye Shapira.

00:01:57.850 --> 00:01:59.550
dem meydlshn nomen.

00:01:59.644 --> 00:02:03.610
AND uh zog mir, h- du host bridern OR shvester?

00:02:03.639 --> 00:02:06.100
kh'hob gehat. tsum badoyern hob ikh gehat.

00:02:06.600 --> 00:02:09.400
kh'hob gehat eyn bruder un dray shvester.

00:02:09.427 --> 00:02:12.552
di nomen fun ale? az du kenst.

00:02:11.479 --> 00:02:12.597
YAKOV,

00:02:12.773 --> 00:02:13.744
YAKOV?

00:02:13.550 --> 00:02:14.650
yo, Yankl.

00:02:14.816 --> 00:02:16.009
di eltste?

00:02:15.939 --> 00:02:17.470
der eltster, yo, Yankl.

00:02:18.139 --> 00:02:22.434
nokh dem iz geven eh nokh dem iz Khane.

00:02:22.992 --> 00:02:26.816
nokh dem iz geven NECHAMA un nokh dem iz geven SARAH.

00:02:28.286 --> 00:02:31.838
vos hot pasirt tsu dayn mishpokhe?

00:02:30.492 --> 00:02:31.845
der elterer

00:02:31.896 --> 00:02:36.081
der elterer bruder iz umgekumen in Daytshland, ober ikh veys nit vu.

00:02:36.531 --> 00:02:42.081
tsvey shvester mit di mamen zaynen umgekumen in Ponar, in Vilne,

00:02:43.631 --> 00:02:46.531
in nayntsn tsvey un fertsik.

00:02:48.231 --> 00:02:53.181
di yingste shvester iz umgekumen in STUTTHOF

00:02:54.931 --> 00:02:56.881
dray teg far der bafrayung.

00:02:58.581 --> 00:03:04.331
da- di mame iz oykh umgekumen in Ponar. der tate iz umgekumen in Kloge,

00:03:04.431 --> 00:03:06.431
dos iz Letland,

00:03:07.631 --> 00:03:09.381
in a lager

00:03:09.381 --> 00:03:17.931
vu me hot ge- m'hot zey, m'hot genumen mentshn, m'hot avekgefirt in vald un geheysn onhakn holts.

00:03:18.431 --> 00:03:21.581
az di mentshn hobn ongehakt di holts hot men zey geshosn.

00:03:21.587 --> 00:03:22.361
ale?

00:03:22.381 --> 00:03:28.431
yo. nokh dem hot men genumen di iberike mentshn, un yeder eynem hot men geheysn nemen a klots

00:03:28.431 --> 00:03:30.281
un kumen tsurik

00:03:30.281 --> 00:03:33.681
un zikh leygn oyf zayn klots vos er hot gebrakht.

00:03:33.681 --> 00:03:36.231
un zey hobn geshosn in kop.

00:03:37.031 --> 00:03:42.581
zey hobn ale mentshn azoy oysgeleygt biz vanet es hot zikh gebildet a shayter-hoyfn.

00:03:42.581 --> 00:03:45.081
un zey hobn untergetsundn di mentshn.

00:03:45.081 --> 00:03:48.181
teyl zaynen shoyn geven toyt un teyl zaynen nokh geven lebedik.

00:03:48.181 --> 00:03:51.031
un zey hobn farbrent di mentshn azoy oyfn shayter-hoyfn.

00:03:51.610 --> 00:03:53.710
ikh vil visn

00:03:53.710 --> 00:03:55.860
uhm, vegn dayn uh,

00:03:55.960 --> 00:04:00.060
az du hot geven a kind, zog mir, in der heym.

00:04:00.160 --> 00:04:03.310
RELIGIOUS? zeyer RELIGIOUS? nisht azoy?

00:04:03.310 --> 00:04:08.960
di muter iz geven zeyer religIOUS, vayl zi hot geshtamt fun zeyer a religyezer familye. der foter iz nit geven azoy.

00:04:08.965 --> 00:04:11.322
d- d- di muter hot a sheytl gevorn?

00:04:10.467 --> 00:04:11.982
NO NO NO, nit keyn sheytl.

00:04:11.628 --> 00:04:12.521
nisht a sheytl.

00:04:11.982 --> 00:04:15.547
zi iz geven religyez ober on a sheytl ge-, nit fanatish religyez.

00:04:16.047 --> 00:04:19.015
un der foter nit azoy, ober mir hobn gefirt a,

00:04:19.015 --> 00:04:24.000
mir hobn gefirt a virtshaft vos iz geven fleyshik bazunder, milkhik bazunder.

00:04:24.000 --> 00:04:25.741
opgehit shabes opgehit,

00:04:25.741 --> 00:04:27.757
azoy vi s'hot zikh a mol gefirt zikh.

00:04:27.510 --> 00:04:28.562
peysekh?

00:04:28.410 --> 00:04:32.960
oh! peysekh iz geven oysgeramt di shtub, alts peysekhdik gemakht, reyn.

00:04:32.910 --> 00:04:34.510
AND shabes?

00:04:34.510 --> 00:04:35.692
ale shabes?

00:04:35.505 --> 00:04:36.856
shabes, gehit shabes.

00:04:36.948 --> 00:04:41.010
zog mir vos hot geven shabes in dayn hey- dayn heym.

00:04:40.860 --> 00:04:44.910
shabes iz geven azoy: fraytik far nakht, di mame gebentsht likht.

00:04:45.510 --> 00:04:46.763
un der tate...

00:04:46.092 --> 00:04:48.235
mit dayn shvester oder aleyn?

00:04:47.623 --> 00:04:49.807
mit ale k-, ale kinder hobn gemuzt zayn tsuzamen.

00:04:49.869 --> 00:04:50.615
ale kinder.

00:04:50.390 --> 00:04:53.646
ale kinder tsuzamen zitsn bayn tish. keyner hot nit getort feln.

00:04:54.060 --> 00:04:59.010
un me hot gegesn, fraytik tsu nakht hot men gegesn, m'hot ge- opgegesn

00:04:59.010 --> 00:05:03.586
un gemakht kidesh, getrunken vayn, un nokh dem gezungen zmires.

00:05:03.586 --> 00:05:05.341
azoy vi se hot zikh gefirt bay yidn.

00:05:03.800 --> 00:05:05.319
khale? mit khale?

00:05:05.510 --> 00:05:06.256
vos heyst?

00:05:06.225 --> 00:05:07.860
mit mir khale?

00:05:07.410 --> 00:05:11.010
mit khale, zikher, geflokhtene khale. vos far a frage!

00:05:08.292 --> 00:05:08.779
khale?

00:05:09.408 --> 00:05:10.025
yo.

00:05:11.010 --> 00:05:14.610
a khale. azoy vi se firt zikh bay yidn, mit vayn, mit altsgeding tsuzamen.

00:05:14.710 --> 00:05:18.725
vi eh du host gegangen in in a kheyder?

00:05:18.646 --> 00:05:21.596
yo, nit keyn kheyder, dos iz geven aza

00:05:18.725 --> 00:05:19.888
az geven a kind?

00:05:21.596 --> 00:05:23.231
religyeze shul.

00:05:23.231 --> 00:05:24.731
dos hot geheysn

00:05:24.731 --> 00:05:27.731
BEYT ULPANA YAVNE, azoy hot zi geheysn.

00:05:27.731 --> 00:05:29.731
finf yor hob ikh dortn gelernt.

00:05:30.581 --> 00:05:34.831
un fun dortn bin ikh ongekumen in a yi- in a hebreishe shul

00:05:34.831 --> 00:05:38.331
vos zi hot geheysn BEYT Seyfer Amomi Al Sheym Epshteyn.

00:05:38.800 --> 00:05:41.341
az ikh hob geendikt di shule bin ikh arayn in gimnazye.

00:05:41.346 --> 00:05:42.143
vifl yor?

00:05:42.400 --> 00:05:43.767
ikh hob eh,

00:05:43.767 --> 00:05:46.038
ikh hob gelernt zeks yor, hob ikh gelernt.

00:05:45.866 --> 00:05:47.155
in gantsn zeks yor?

00:05:46.755 --> 00:05:51.300
NO, nokh dem bin ikh ariber in gimnazye, hob gelernt nokh dray, nayn yor hob ikh gelernt tsuzamen.

00:05:51.300 --> 00:05:59.950
ober azoy vi mayn foter hot mir gedarft eh hot ge- se se hot genoytikt in mayn hilf, hob ikh ibergerisn dem lernen un bin gegangen helfn dem foter in der arbet.

00:05:59.800 --> 00:06:02.069
yo, eh vi alt eh bistu?

00:06:02.151 --> 00:06:03.100
yetst?

00:06:03.400 --> 00:06:05.500
yetst bin ikh

00:06:05.500 --> 00:06:06.664
iber akhtsik.

00:06:06.691 --> 00:06:07.350
iber.

00:06:07.373 --> 00:06:08.144
a dank got.

00:06:08.150 --> 00:06:11.200
danken got iz emes. uhm

00:06:11.350 --> 00:06:14.950
uh in der heym, du host gevust az du bist a yid?

00:06:14.900 --> 00:06:16.150
oh, yo!

00:06:15.863 --> 00:06:16.312
yo.

00:06:16.312 --> 00:06:19.608
host gegangen in shul arayn mit eh mit dayn uh...

00:06:16.574 --> 00:06:17.257
zikher!

00:06:18.972 --> 00:06:21.404
shabes flegn mir geyn in shul mitn tatn.

00:06:21.672 --> 00:06:22.483
nor...

00:06:21.697 --> 00:06:22.559
shabes.

00:06:22.559 --> 00:06:25.900
shabes, nor shabes.

00:06:23.850 --> 00:06:26.362
Yosl, du AND di AND di...

00:06:26.150 --> 00:06:28.428
dag- i- da- nor, di meydlekh nit.

00:06:28.450 --> 00:06:28.991
n- n-

00:06:29.051 --> 00:06:32.400
nor neyn, n- nor dem, zin, der der elterer bruder.

00:06:29.385 --> 00:06:30.453
nor di, nor...

00:06:32.450 --> 00:06:33.807
der yingerer bruder heyst es.

00:06:34.092 --> 00:06:35.116
AND nisht di meydlekh.

00:06:35.250 --> 00:06:36.931
meydlekh nit. di meyd-...

00:06:35.989 --> 00:06:37.654
o- oyf yont- yontoyvim?

00:06:37.191 --> 00:06:41.191
yontoyvim yo. yontoyvim iz di gantse familye gegangen in shul arayn. yontoyvim yo.

00:06:38.777 --> 00:06:39.283
ale?

00:06:41.232 --> 00:06:46.850
in der heym hostu h- eh vi, zog mir vegn Vilne.

00:06:47.660 --> 00:06:49.938
Vilne iz a shtot velkhe yidn

00:06:49.938 --> 00:06:52.710
z- hobn gelebt in ir finf hundert yor.

00:06:53.660 --> 00:06:57.960
un di batsiung fun di bafelkerung iz geven nit keyn shlekhte.

00:06:58.060 --> 00:07:02.110
far vos? s'iz geven a groyse tsol yidn geven un di,

00:07:02.410 --> 00:07:05.510
a sakh aynvoyner hobn gearbet bay di yidn.

00:07:05.960 --> 00:07:07.910
vos hot zikh nisht shlekht batsoygn. 

00:07:07.910 --> 00:07:09.260
biz van?

00:07:09.260 --> 00:07:12.060
bizn nayn un draysikstn yor,

00:07:12.325 --> 00:07:17.175
hot zikh ongehoybn di milkho-, farn nayn un draysikstn yor iz gekumen RYDZ-ŚMIGŁY tsu der makht, a general.

00:07:17.175 --> 00:07:19.725
damolst hot zikh ongehoybn der antisemitizm.

00:07:19.725 --> 00:07:22.575
ober a, biz dan, ven PIŁSUDSKI hot gelebt...

00:07:22.479 --> 00:07:23.242
gornisht?

00:07:23.475 --> 00:07:25.375
iz geven zeyer gut far yidn.

00:07:25.325 --> 00:07:30.375
AND zog mir, vos host- uh vo- vos far a arbet host dayn tate getun?

00:07:29.525 --> 00:07:33.400
uh er hot gehat a MOVING OFFICE.

00:07:33.325 --> 00:07:34.925
zog mir vos iz dos.

00:07:34.525 --> 00:07:38.156
eh ekspeditsye, nor ikh veys nit vi dos tsu zogn, vi az-, a MOVING OFFICE, vos hot

00:07:38.156 --> 00:07:41.875
fir- aribergefirt, transportirt skhoyre fun eyn plats oyfn tsveytn plats.

00:07:42.575 --> 00:07:44.125
etlekhe yor?

00:07:44.175 --> 00:07:47.075
eh bizn nayn un draysikstn yor.

00:07:46.375 --> 00:07:50.075
AND d- dayn mishpokhe hot geven in Vilne?

00:07:49.925 --> 00:07:51.925
ale in Vilne geven di gantse tsayt.

00:07:51.925 --> 00:07:54.775
bizn nayn un draysikstn yor zaynen mir ale geven tsuzamen.

00:07:55.175 --> 00:07:59.325
in nayn un draysikstn yor bin ikh mobilizirt gevorn in poylisher armey,

00:08:00.225 --> 00:08:02.675
un ikh hob gekemft bay Varshe,

00:08:02.975 --> 00:08:06.625
un dortn hot men undz genumen in krigs-gefangenshaft,

00:08:06.827 --> 00:08:09.977
un me hot undz avekgeshikt in Daytshland,

00:08:09.977 --> 00:08:11.177
OSTPREUSSEN.

00:08:11.927 --> 00:08:14.827
un ikh bin geven in a lager in Rizenburg.

00:08:14.827 --> 00:08:17.877
mir zaynen geven tsvelf toyznt mentshn.

00:08:17.877 --> 00:08:24.478
ober damolst, s'iz geven der onheyb, hot nokh nit segregirt yidn un polyakn. ale zaynen geven tsuzamen.

00:08:24.327 --> 00:08:25.378
ale tsuzamen.

00:08:24.827 --> 00:08:26.369
ale tsuzamen zay-

00:08:25.378 --> 00:08:26.876
uh ey- eyn minut, eyn minut, ersht.

00:08:27.086 --> 00:08:28.649
uhm frier fun dem tsayt,

00:08:28.649 --> 00:08:30.387
du host gearbet mit dayn tate?

00:08:30.176 --> 00:08:31.038
yo yo.

00:08:30.653 --> 00:08:32.177
zog, zog mir v- uh

00:08:32.177 --> 00:08:33.677
vos du host geton.

00:08:32.225 --> 00:08:33.677
ikh hob gearbet ba-

00:08:33.677 --> 00:08:36.061
ikh hob gearbet der ekspeditsye mit mayn foter.

00:08:35.627 --> 00:08:37.477
vi alt host geven?

00:08:37.277 --> 00:08:38.877
damolst geven?

00:08:38.977 --> 00:08:44.077
zekhtsn yor, fuftsn yor, bay, glaykh vi, nokhn shule bin ikh avekgegangen arbetn.

00:08:44.127 --> 00:08:46.077
un kh'hob oykh gearbet,

00:08:46.277 --> 00:08:48.727
in nayntsn tsvey un draysik,

00:08:49.477 --> 00:08:52.277
hot men gemakht a boykot oyf daytshishe skhoyres.

00:08:52.877 --> 00:08:57.127
az yidn zoln nit brengen fun Daytshland keyn skhoyres.

00:08:57.327 --> 00:09:00.427
ikh hob gearbet tsuzamen mit dokter Vigodski,

00:09:00.427 --> 00:09:03.577
dos iz geven der forzitser fun der ke-, Vilner kehile. 

00:09:04.277 --> 00:09:07.308
hob ikh mit im tsu- eh er iz geven der forzitser fun undzer komitet.

00:09:07.308 --> 00:09:11.427
un azoy vi ikh hob gearbet in di ekspeditsye hob ikh gehat batsiungen

00:09:11.427 --> 00:09:15.177
mit poylishe baamte velkhe hobn gearbet in tsol-amt.

00:09:16.027 --> 00:09:17.990
un zey flegn mir ibergebn a list

00:09:17.990 --> 00:09:21.127
velkhe yidn es brengen daytshishe skhoyres.

00:09:21.577 --> 00:09:25.277
un ikh fleg di list avekgebn dokter Vigodski, olev-hasholem

00:09:25.527 --> 00:09:32.277
un er fleg shikn mentshn vorenen di yidn, di sokhrim, az zey zoln nit araynbrengen keyn skhoyres fun Daytshland.

00:09:33.927 --> 00:09:38.377
tsum badoyern, nit ale hot dos geholfn, nor bay, teylvayz hot dos geholfn.

00:09:38.727 --> 00:09:43.258
un un dos iz geven mayn arbet, mayn arbet iz geven ikh hob gearbet in, in, in

00:09:43.258 --> 00:09:48.327
in kantor hob ikh gearbet, in kantor, in droysn hob ikh gearbet, vi a mol, vi di arbet hot gefodert hob ikh gearbet.

00:09:48.116 --> 00:09:49.716
AND eh zog mir yetst

00:09:49.916 --> 00:09:52.066
uh in THE ARMY, du host geganen

00:09:52.066 --> 00:09:54.016
in di, in THE POLISH ARMY,

00:09:54.167 --> 00:09:54.726
yo.

00:09:54.226 --> 00:09:55.841
AND zog mir vos hot pasirt.

00:09:55.534 --> 00:09:56.719
oh in nayntsn...

00:09:56.097 --> 00:09:57.963
ale tsuzamen, yidn un goyim...

00:09:57.876 --> 00:10:01.974
yo, in nayntsn nayn un draysik, bin ikh mobilizirt gevorn damolst in (UNK plen)

00:10:01.974 --> 00:10:04.416
mir zaynen geven in a lager in Rizenburg. 

00:10:04.602 --> 00:10:06.183
mir zaynen geven tsvelf toyznt man

00:10:06.183 --> 00:10:08.016
un s'iz geven fir velt-kikhn,

00:10:08.016 --> 00:10:09.466
fir feld-kikhn.

00:10:09.566 --> 00:10:14.166
un fir feld-kikhn kenen ba- ba- ba- bashpayzn tsvelf toyznt mentshn.

00:10:14.166 --> 00:10:16.966
fleg men zeks a zeyger in der fri oyfshteyn,

00:10:17.616 --> 00:10:20.466
un zikh shteln in rey,

00:10:20.466 --> 00:10:22.966
tsu krign esn. der esn iz bashtanen

00:10:22.966 --> 00:10:25.566
fun a bisl broyne vaser mit eyn shtikl broyt.

00:10:26.566 --> 00:10:29.516
un tsvelf a zeyger fleg men oysrufn da-

00:10:29.516 --> 00:10:32.516
frishtik iz geendikt, yetst vet ir esn mitog.

00:10:32.516 --> 00:10:37.566
der mitog iz bashtanen fun a bisl reyne, vareme vaser mit eyn shtikl broyt.

00:10:37.416 --> 00:10:38.616
di zelbe?

00:10:38.466 --> 00:10:41.066
yo. in etlekhe teg

00:10:41.066 --> 00:10:44.066
oyb emetser hot bakumen a shtikl broyt iz er geven a gliklekher.

00:10:44.416 --> 00:10:46.916
nor mir tsufelik hot opgeglikt

00:10:46.916 --> 00:10:49.140
farn araynfaln in plen

00:10:49.216 --> 00:10:55.566
hot men tseteylt ales vos iz geven, hob ikh gekhapt nor broyt. andere hobn gekhapt andere zakhn. ikh hob gekhapt nor tsvey lebelekh broyt.

00:10:55.766 --> 00:11:01.716
un dos hot mir geholfn oystsuhaltn di shlekhte tsayt bizn antloyfn fun lager.

00:11:01.716 --> 00:11:03.377
mit tsvey leblekh broyt.

00:11:03.452 --> 00:11:05.332
dos iz geven tayerer vi gold!

00:11:07.316 --> 00:11:11.916
dos heyst, dos heyst bay, z- der der lebn in lager iz geven zeyer a shlekhter, on esn,

00:11:12.766 --> 00:11:19.516
un vaser iz geven, fir kranen iz geven vaser in gantsn tsu toyznt-, nit keyn vaser, nit keyn esn, gornit geven. 

00:11:20.816 --> 00:11:23.151
du host gearbet dortn in di lager?

00:11:22.412 --> 00:11:25.766
NO NO, s'iz di ershte teg fun der milkhome geven.

00:11:25.766 --> 00:11:26.896
dos iz glaykh di ershte teg...

00:11:25.950 --> 00:11:27.827
vi lang host geven in di lager?

00:11:27.347 --> 00:11:27.823
oh.

00:11:27.823 --> 00:11:29.669
in lager bin ikh geven tsen teg.

00:11:29.977 --> 00:11:32.977
un me hot undz aroysgefirt oyf arbet,

00:11:34.427 --> 00:11:37.727
ontsulodn holts, kletser. groyse kletser onlodn.

00:11:37.727 --> 00:11:39.977
akhtsn mentshn hobn gekayklt a klots.

00:11:40.827 --> 00:11:46.877
un mir zaynen gekumen oyfn ban-stantsye, un me hot gekayklt di kletser. m'hot ongelodevet vagones holts, kletser,

00:11:47.127 --> 00:11:50.177
tsu firn farrikhtn a brik in Ostrolenko.

00:11:51.027 --> 00:11:57.277
ikh hob gehert vi di poylishe ban-arbeter hobn geredt tsvishn zikh poylish, un azoy vi ikh hob farshtanen

00:11:57.777 --> 00:12:01.327
hob ikh farshtanen az zey forn in Ostrolenko firn di holts.

00:12:01.477 --> 00:12:04.127
hob ikh gezogt tsu maynem a khaver, a Vilner,

00:12:04.727 --> 00:12:05.977
"lomir antloyfn,

00:12:06.077 --> 00:12:08.777
anit vet men shtarbn fun hunger. s'iz nito keyn oysveg".

00:12:09.277 --> 00:12:11.177
zogt er, "gut, lomir pruvn".

00:12:11.877 --> 00:12:14.027
az me hot gelo- -endikt

00:12:14.027 --> 00:12:18.627
onlodn di holts iz shoyn gevorn halb tunkl, azoy farnakht.

00:12:18.627 --> 00:12:21.177
zey hobn arayngeshprungen in a farlozene hayzke

00:12:21.477 --> 00:12:22.777
un mir hobn zikh bahaltn.

00:12:23.827 --> 00:12:25.427
vu host gehaltn?

00:12:25.027 --> 00:12:26.923
oyfn, oyfn ban-stantsye

00:12:26.923 --> 00:12:29.177
in a farlozene hayzke, mir hobn zikh bahaltn zikh.

00:12:29.427 --> 00:12:32.477
un ikh hob gehert az zey hobn gezogt az tsvelf a zeyger fort op der ban.

00:12:32.927 --> 00:12:33.927
tsvelf bay nakht.

00:12:34.827 --> 00:12:36.477
nu, mir hobn gevart,

00:12:38.227 --> 00:12:40.227
keyn zeyger hob ikh nit gehat.

00:12:40.377 --> 00:12:44.627
nor kh'hob eh gezen vi di ban-arbeter kontrolirn di reder,

00:12:45.127 --> 00:12:47.977
hob ikh farshtanen az zey gey- azoy vi kh'hob gearbet oyfn ban,

00:12:47.977 --> 00:12:51.277
kh'hob gehat di gantse tsayt ba- batsiung mit di ban-arb-, kh'hob gevust di ale zakhn.

00:12:51.527 --> 00:12:53.777
hob ikh farshtanen az zey geyen bald opforn.

00:12:54.927 --> 00:13:00.777
mir hobn zikh arayngekhapt zikh in a leydike budke fun a vagon. s'iz do di budkes, di tormozne budkes heyst dos.

00:13:00.927 --> 00:13:03.427
kh'hob alts gekent, fun banen, zakhn, hob ikh alts gekent.

00:13:03.427 --> 00:13:08.077
do- arayngekhapt in der tormozne budke, mir zaynen gelegn bahaltn. kh'hob aropgelozt zikh oyf der erd, bin ikh bahaltn.

00:13:08.377 --> 00:13:10.227
tsum glik hot men undz nit gefunen,

00:13:10.527 --> 00:13:13.527
un der ban iz opgeforn nokh Ostrolenko.

00:13:14.577 --> 00:13:16.677
mir zaynen gekumen bay Ostrolenko,

00:13:16.677 --> 00:13:20.577
hob ikh gezogt tsu mayn khaver, "lomir aropshpringen, veln mir zikh ophaltn, kenen mir a mol zukhn..."

00:13:20.577 --> 00:13:24.327
hot der ban ongehoybn ts-, pamelekh tsu geyn, zaynen mir aropgeshprungen beyde.

00:13:24.727 --> 00:13:28.827
mir zaynen aropgeshprungen, ober vi geyt men ariber dem taykh? dort iz a groyser taykh

00:13:28.827 --> 00:13:33.127
un der brik iz geven tseruinirt. zey hobn gefirt di holts farrikhtn dem brik.

00:13:34.027 --> 00:13:35.427
zaynen mir gegangen

00:13:35.777 --> 00:13:39.627
noent tsum breg fun vaser un m'hot getrofn a kleyne shifele.

00:13:40.927 --> 00:13:41.986
geven tsu...

00:13:41.369 --> 00:13:42.409
vi kleyn?

00:13:42.727 --> 00:13:46.536
eh far a fish, a fisher-shifele vos me fort oyf FISHING.

00:13:43.300 --> 00:13:44.095
vi groys?

00:13:47.377 --> 00:13:55.527
zaynen mir ara- arayn in f- ober vi nemt, di fi- di shifl iz geven tsugebundn mit a, mit a hil- mit a dos, mit a, mit a shtrik.

00:13:55.677 --> 00:13:59.277
m'hot dokh gornit gehat bay zikh. hot men genumen tsvey shteyner, ibergeklapt dem shtrik.

00:13:59.527 --> 00:14:01.827
un mit di hent hot men zikh aribergeshift oyfn tsveytn zayt.

00:14:02.227 --> 00:14:09.627
mir zaynen gekumen oyfn tsveytn zayt iz azoy. fun dem zayt zaynen geven di daytshn, oyfn tsveytn zayt zaynen geven di rusn, der taykh iz geven der ibergang.

00:14:09.977 --> 00:14:11.427
hobn undz di rusn farhaltn.

00:14:12.527 --> 00:14:20.977
di rusn farhaltn, hobn zey mir gefre- gefregt vos tuen mir, vos makhn mir. hobn mir gezogt, zest dokh, mir zaynen, poylishe zakhn, mir zaynen antlofn fun krigs-gefangenshaft-lager.

00:14:22.077 --> 00:14:24.827
un er hot gezen take rikhtik vi mir zeen oys,

00:14:25.127 --> 00:14:28.477
oysgehungert, oysgematert un un di poylishe zakhn.

00:14:28.477 --> 00:14:30.377
zogt er, geyt aheym.

00:14:30.827 --> 00:14:31.977
bafrayt!

00:14:32.781 --> 00:14:33.489
tsu Vilne.

00:14:33.527 --> 00:14:35.927
der zelner. der rusisher zelner hot undz bafrayt.

00:14:36.327 --> 00:14:40.577
n-, zaynen mir gegangen vayter, ober damolst bin ikh shoyn gegangen

00:14:40.677 --> 00:14:42.127
biz Lomzhe

00:14:42.127 --> 00:14:44.327
bin ikh dergangen. mir zaynen beyde dergangen tsu fus.

00:14:44.627 --> 00:14:46.477
s'hot gedoyert etlekhe teg.

00:14:46.477 --> 00:14:50.677
geshpayzt hobn mir zikh mit roye kartofl.

00:14:50.777 --> 00:14:51.884
mir flegn arop-...

00:14:51.301 --> 00:14:52.660
vos host geesn?

00:14:52.827 --> 00:14:54.826
ot dos zog ikh, dos zog ikh vos kh'hob gegesn.

00:14:52.863 --> 00:14:53.545
in dem tsayt?

00:14:54.977 --> 00:14:56.177
roye kartofl.

00:14:56.177 --> 00:14:58.577
un mir hobn oykh gegesn beryoze,

00:14:58.577 --> 00:15:00.577
(kore f-) beryoze fun di boymer.

00:15:00.577 --> 00:15:04.077
yunge beryozke. dos iz zeyer gezunt un zis. me ken es fardayen.

00:15:04.227 --> 00:15:07.677
un tsu-, a mol hobn mir getrofn tsuker-burikes oyf di felder.

00:15:07.777 --> 00:15:09.877
dos hobn mir zikh bashpayzt zikh.

00:15:09.877 --> 00:15:13.527
mir zaynen ongekumen in Lomzhe ober keyn koyekh hobn mir nit gehat mer tsu geyn.

00:15:13.827 --> 00:15:18.027
hobn mir oyfgezukht a a a balegole, a mentsh mit a ferd

00:15:18.027 --> 00:15:21.527
un gebetn er zol undz firn in Byalistok.

00:15:21.527 --> 00:15:25.577
vayl in Lomzhe iz geven tseshtert der ban, nit geven keyn bavegung fun di banen.

00:15:25.577 --> 00:15:27.027
m'hot (im) bombardirt.

00:15:28.327 --> 00:15:31.577
gut, hobn mir im batsolt, me hot undz gefirt keyn Byalistok.

00:15:31.327 --> 00:15:33.655
mit vos hot, hostu im batsolt?

00:15:32.777 --> 00:15:34.281
kh'hob gehat gelt bay zikh.

00:15:34.163 --> 00:15:34.513
ah!

00:15:34.281 --> 00:15:36.177
farn araynfaln in plen

00:15:36.227 --> 00:15:41.227
hot der general tseteylt, alemen gegebn, ikh gedenk nit, toyznt zlotes, tsi toyznt finf hundert zlotes.

00:15:41.227 --> 00:15:43.527
hot er, un aleyn hot er zikh dershosn, der general.

00:15:43.777 --> 00:15:46.577
er hot gezogt, farn koved fun Poyln

00:15:47.377 --> 00:15:48.977
un di foter-land

00:15:48.977 --> 00:15:50.577
gey ikh nit in plen.

00:15:50.889 --> 00:15:53.877
hot alemen tseteylt di gelt, di broyt vos er hot gehat,

00:15:54.127 --> 00:15:55.827
un aleyn hot er zikh dershosn zikh.

00:15:57.977 --> 00:16:01.827
kumendik in Byalistok iz geven azoy far tog.

00:16:02.127 --> 00:16:05.227
vu geyt men? in di poylishe zakhn, me vet dokh undz arestirn.

00:16:05.327 --> 00:16:07.377
me tor dokh nit arumgeyn in di poylishe zakhn.

00:16:07.427 --> 00:16:10.077
zaynen mir avek in a park, in a vinkl fun park,

00:16:10.077 --> 00:16:12.677
zikh bahaltn zikh un zikh gezetst oyf a benkl.

00:16:14.127 --> 00:16:16.727
mir zaynen fun midkeyt zaynen mir ayngeshlofn.

00:16:17.177 --> 00:16:18.472
mit di zelbe kleyder?

00:16:18.427 --> 00:16:20.427
altsdi- un do iz di geshikhte, di historye.

00:16:20.427 --> 00:16:21.368
di zelbe kleyder.

00:16:21.368 --> 00:16:23.027
f- mir zaynen ayngeshlofn.

00:16:23.227 --> 00:16:25.277
mir hobn zikh oyfgekhapt un s'iz geven

00:16:25.277 --> 00:16:29.427
mistome tsen a zeyger, vayl eh mir hobn gezen froyen mit kinder geyen shpatsirn in park.

00:16:29.777 --> 00:16:33.577
un zey hobn derzen poylishe krigs-gefangene, zaynen zey tsugelofn fregn,

00:16:33.577 --> 00:16:36.577
"efsher hostu gezen mayn tatn, efsher hostu gezen mayn man, efsher..."

00:16:37.077 --> 00:16:43.627
nu, kh'hob zey alemen geentfert di zelbe e- s'iz geven a groyse tsetuml, un s'iz geven a groyse bombardirung, me hot shtark bombardirt, yo, du kenst zen.

00:16:44.440 --> 00:16:46.177
mir zaynen koym antlofn mitn lebn,

00:16:47.277 --> 00:16:48.777
ober vos tut men vayter?

00:16:49.377 --> 00:16:52.427
iz tsugekumen a, tsugekumen tsu undz a yidishe froy un gezogt,

00:16:52.577 --> 00:16:54.477
"kumt mit mir tsu mir in shtub".

00:16:54.677 --> 00:16:55.777
in Byalistok.

00:16:57.477 --> 00:16:59.477
mir zaynen avek tsu ir in shtub.

00:16:59.477 --> 00:17:02.427
un zi hot undz gegebn zikh optsuvashn.

00:17:02.427 --> 00:17:05.527
oprazirn zikh. mir zaynen geven nit razirt.

00:17:05.727 --> 00:17:07.927
hot zi gefregt tsi mir esn

00:17:07.927 --> 00:17:09.377
nit keyn koshere.

00:17:09.377 --> 00:17:11.977
nu, mir hobn gehat an oysveg? mir hobn gegesn vos me hot undz gegebn.

00:17:12.277 --> 00:17:16.977
der iker, der esn, mir hobn eh mir hobn zikh gut ongegesn ober mir hobn es nit getort ton,

00:17:16.977 --> 00:17:20.927
vayl nokh azoy fil tsayt hungern tor men nit esn mit eyn mol tsu der zet.

00:17:20.977 --> 00:17:22.677
hobn mir gebrokhn.

00:17:23.427 --> 00:17:24.727
tsurik.

00:17:25.177 --> 00:17:27.077
arayn in (vane m-)

00:17:27.077 --> 00:17:31.127
zi hot undz, zi hot zeyer nebekh gelitn fun undz. mir hobn ge- farmakht umetum.

00:17:32.077 --> 00:17:33.827
zogt zi, "rut zikh op".

00:17:33.827 --> 00:17:37.477
s'iz gekumen fir a zeyger zogt zi, "mayn man darf kumen fun der arbet

00:17:38.177 --> 00:17:41.627
un ikh ken aykh nit haltn vayl mayn man iz a parteyner.

00:17:41.627 --> 00:17:43.627
er arbet in komunistisher partey".

00:17:44.427 --> 00:17:45.227
farfaln.

00:17:45.577 --> 00:17:50.527
nor zi hot zikh dervust un gezogt az tsvelf a zeyger bay nakht geyt op a ban nokh Vilne.

00:17:52.527 --> 00:17:54.664
mir zaynen avek vayter in park. vu geyt men?

00:17:54.664 --> 00:17:58.277
s'iz nito vos zi ken... er lozt undz nit arayn. ale hobn moyre gehat far di rusishe.

00:17:58.727 --> 00:18:02.977
zaynen mir avek in park un gevart. yeder sh-, yeder minut iz geven bay undz a yor.

00:18:03.677 --> 00:18:08.477
az mir hobn derlebt di tsayt, s'iz gekumen halb tsvelf zaynen mir avek, avek oyfn vokzal.

00:18:09.527 --> 00:18:13.831
di shprakh hobn mir gekent, hobn mir zikh dervust zikh velkhe ban es geyt oyf Vilne.

00:18:13.831 --> 00:18:16.400
mir zaynen arayn in ban un gezetst zikh, azoy vi ale zitsn.

00:18:19.000 --> 00:18:20.677
oyfn veg

00:18:20.677 --> 00:18:23.827
hobn mir zikh tsuzamen geredt mit tsvey rusishe yidn.

00:18:23.827 --> 00:18:26.127
neyn, ne-, vart. s'iz geven shpeter iz es geven.

00:18:26.227 --> 00:18:29.477
zaynen mir gezesn ba- mir zaynen geforn, mir zaynen gekumen biz Grodne.

00:18:29.827 --> 00:18:32.277
in Grodne zaynen arayn roytarmeyer,

00:18:32.527 --> 00:18:33.577
un geshrien,

00:18:33.600 --> 00:18:36.077
"poylishe krigs-gefangene aroys!"

00:18:36.577 --> 00:18:39.327
mir zaynen geven in mundirn, me hot keyn breyre nit gehat.

00:18:39.777 --> 00:18:45.427
bin ikh aroysgelofn fun tsveytn, ikh bin geven bakant mit di vagones, dos hot gev- dos hot mir a bisl geholfn.

00:18:46.077 --> 00:18:53.427
bin ikh aroys fun tsveytn zayt, zikh geshtelt zikh fun di fintstern zayt fun vokzal. veyst dokh der vokzal geyt eyn zayt baloykhtn un fun tsveytn zayt iz tunkl. 

00:18:54.077 --> 00:18:55.227
un hob ge-

00:18:55.577 --> 00:18:59.677
avekgeleygt zikh bay der erd un gevart, az der ban vet opgeyn vel ikh zikh aroyfkhapn.

00:18:59.677 --> 00:19:01.827
mayn khaver iz arayn in a,

00:19:01.827 --> 00:19:02.977
in a TOILET

00:19:03.177 --> 00:19:04.177
zikh bahaltn.

00:19:05.227 --> 00:19:07.727
ikh bin aroyf ts- der ban hot ongehoybn tsu rirn.

00:19:07.777 --> 00:19:10.127
hob ikh zikh gekhapt farn hentl un aroyf tsurik.

00:19:10.527 --> 00:19:13.677
un avekgezetst zikh lebn di zelbe yidn vos hobn gezesn frier.

00:19:14.627 --> 00:19:18.027
un kh'hob gezukht mayn khaver, tsum badoyern, im hot men aropgenumen.

00:19:18.427 --> 00:19:24.400
un er iz umgekumen in rusishn plen iz er umgekumen. in rusishn gefangenshaft iz er umgekumen.

00:19:24.777 --> 00:19:30.577
az mir zaynen geforn vayter, hob ikh gezen di shpil fun Grodne, hob ikh getrakht, in Vilne ken ikh shoyn nit araynforn.

00:19:30.577 --> 00:19:32.427
vayl me vet dokh mir vider arestirn.

00:19:32.627 --> 00:19:34.559
hob ikh zikh opgeredt mit di tsvey yidn,

00:19:34.559 --> 00:19:37.127
gegebn mayn adres fun Vilne,

00:19:37.227 --> 00:19:40.827
un gebetn zey zoln onzogn mayn froy az ikh leb,

00:19:41.027 --> 00:19:45.277
un ikh gefin zikh in di un in di shtetl. vayl ikh hob di gegnt zeyer gut gekent.

00:19:45.427 --> 00:19:46.912
Landverove hot es geheysn.

00:19:46.912 --> 00:19:49.227
dos iz finf un tsvantsik kilometer far Vilne.

00:19:50.227 --> 00:19:51.527
un ikh bin,

00:19:51.527 --> 00:19:54.377
s'iz gekumen in Landverove, hot zikh geshtelt, bin ikh aropgelofn

00:19:54.396 --> 00:19:55.477
fun ban.

00:19:55.477 --> 00:19:57.427
ober vu geyt men vayter?

00:19:57.427 --> 00:19:59.977
bin ikh avek in a shule, in a sinagoge. 

00:20:00.477 --> 00:20:03.220
nu, kh'hob geredt dem rov, kh'hob im dertseylt az s-

00:20:02.720 --> 00:20:03.630
in in Vilne?

00:20:03.677 --> 00:20:06.292
NO, NO, nit in Vil-, NO, tsu Vilne iz nokh vayt.

00:20:03.992 --> 00:20:04.370
NO.

00:20:04.370 --> 00:20:05.204
nisht in Vilne?

00:20:05.649 --> 00:20:06.740
vi hot dos geven?

00:20:06.750 --> 00:20:11.277
Landverove heyst di shtetl. a kleyne shtetl finf un tsvantsik kilometer far Vilne.

00:20:12.277 --> 00:20:14.677
zogt er, er ken undz gornit helfn.

00:20:15.227 --> 00:20:18.048
vayl er hot moyre far di rusn tsu ton aza min zakh.

00:20:18.048 --> 00:20:21.406
gebn zakhn, do iz a, iberton a soldat, dos iz a geferlekhe zakh.

00:20:21.461 --> 00:20:23.477
tsugekumen tsu undz a yid, zogt er,

00:20:24.177 --> 00:20:25.227
"kum mit mir".

00:20:26.127 --> 00:20:27.627
hot er avekgefirt aheym.

00:20:28.327 --> 00:20:29.627
gegebn esn.

00:20:29.677 --> 00:20:31.327
AND di kleyder nisht?

00:20:31.000 --> 00:20:33.062
AND kleyder hot er moyre gehat. kleyder nit.

00:20:33.062 --> 00:20:34.311
gegebn esn.

00:20:34.311 --> 00:20:36.277
undz hot men geheysn bahaltn oyfn oyvn.

00:20:36.527 --> 00:20:40.377
in in di kleyne shtetlekh iz do groyse oyvns azoy,

00:20:40.377 --> 00:20:43.477
ver veyst. kh'hob mikh avekgeleygt oyfn oyvn un bin ayngeshlofn azoy.

00:20:44.477 --> 00:20:49.677
oyf morgn, hot mir der yid gezogt, "dayn froy iz gekumen".

00:20:51.377 --> 00:20:54.527
mayn froy iz gekumen mit zakhn, mit tsivile zakhn.

00:20:54.877 --> 00:20:58.958
zey zaynen zeyer gute yidn. zey hobn ongezogt ir, zi iz geven tsetumlt fun UNK. 

00:20:58.958 --> 00:21:01.918
"zolst nemen skarpetn, zolst nemen shikh, zolst nemen hoyzn".

00:21:01.204 --> 00:21:02.577
vi hostu eh

00:21:02.577 --> 00:21:05.177
zog mir fun dayn froy, eh eyn minut.

00:21:04.315 --> 00:21:05.355
nu nu, nu nu.

00:21:05.177 --> 00:21:06.377
di nomen?

00:21:06.577 --> 00:21:07.677
m- vemen nomen?

00:21:07.427 --> 00:21:08.627
da- dayn froy.

00:21:08.527 --> 00:21:09.827
ah SARAH.

00:21:09.827 --> 00:21:11.577
ikh hob dir gegebn dem bild.

00:21:11.677 --> 00:21:12.121
AND

00:21:11.876 --> 00:21:12.413
SARAH

00:21:12.352 --> 00:21:15.329
SARAH? AND uh vi lang farheyrat?

00:21:15.548 --> 00:21:16.548
in dem tsayt?

00:21:15.927 --> 00:21:18.477
fun zibn un draysikstn yor. tsvey yor farheyrat geven.

00:21:18.227 --> 00:21:19.217
tsvey yor.

00:21:19.018 --> 00:21:19.759
tsvey yor yo.

00:21:19.512 --> 00:21:23.059
nisht uh nisht keyn uh kinder gehat?

00:21:22.773 --> 00:21:24.377
NO, nit gehat keyn kinder. tsvey yor.

00:21:24.827 --> 00:21:28.427
